{"tid":581734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【廣深高鐵大停駛‧深圳北站】一聽到延誤乘客即搶飯盒 港人執輸捱肚餓","createTime":"2018-03-05T14:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T23:30:47.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9ad14b03811442c2731079b647e3e4113b994eab","tid":581734,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180305/large/1520257183_a08c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180305%2Flarge%2F1520257183_a08c.jpg&h=48aa560d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翟太和友人到普寧探親，不料今日回程遇上列車故障，延誤個半鐘才返到深圳。<br />\n<br />\n廣深高鐵今日發生故障大停駛，多個班次接近癱瘓，搞了大半天到下午3時逐步回復正常，但有港人下午4時半坐高鐵南下到深圳北站，仍然面對延誤問題，足足遲了一個多小時才返到深圳，叫苦連天。<br />\n<br />\n任職保險的港人翟太(53歲)，日前與朋友到廣東普寧探鄉間父親，今天乘坐由福州南開深圳北高鐵，在普寧開車時間為4點30分，原定於為6時20分到深圳，不料，當列車5點30分駛至惠州南時，車廂廣播「信號故障需延誤」，乘客可以選擇下車轉乘其他交通工具，或繼續呆等。<br />\n<br />\n廣播後，由於大部份乘客均不知道停車會停幾耐，故出現大批乘客「搶飯盒」潮，惟輪到翟太購買時，飯盒已搶光，她們只好忍着肚餓繼續等，連食水都供應不足。幸而列車最終只延誤了約一個半小時，她們甫步出站，翟太已大叫：「好肚餓！好肚餓！快啲去搵嘢食。」<br />\n<br />\n難得好老公翟先生在深圳北站苦等太太逾一個半鐘，亦毫無怨言。他笑言，太太因為拖着太多行李，遂於開車前通知丈夫到深圳接車，誰知其間因為故障而延誤，翟先生收到太太的訊息後，只無奈在車站附近周圍閒逛，由6時許行到8時才成功接到太太。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180305/large/1520257425_22c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180305%2Flarge%2F1520257425_22c1.jpg&h=0b52adc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180305/large/1520257426_5663.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180305%2Flarge%2F1520257426_5663.jpg&h=eca877bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180305/large/1520257428_a2be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180305%2Flarge%2F1520257428_a2be.jpg&h=6b359fec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180305/57908806\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180305%2F57908806&d=DiGK16OJczRZvohM6yohsNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=1e11ce44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180305%2F57908806&h=464b0b32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180305/57908806</a>"},{"pid":"57077675d03aa76e8a9e1b4d4bc0693ca6710634","tid":581734,"uid":45772,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:57:07.000Z","msg":"記得我哋要有禮貌，唔好人搶我哋又搶。 行行吓街比狗咬，你唔通咬返隻狗轉頭呀？ 記住，愛係我哋最強嘅武器嚟。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9839786c33b1125d07cecd65b7cb98f35596e0c0","tid":581734,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T15:10:14.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"b58edd3cde22a3ea768b0ff3dd8fba4c06431936","tid":581734,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T15:13:23.000Z","msg":"賤種"},{"pid":"bfea59d2448c60f9fa0b983a5fb28a3305202ee8","tid":581734,"uid":35790,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T15:28:17.000Z","msg":"又係新殖民扮香港人"},{"pid":"a9b58f14a83038268faa29617fd18a0a47d23db0","tid":581734,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T01:38:34.000Z","msg":"同野狗搶梗係輸啦"},{"pid":"9d30d9ec1b84a850f6091942457b3595e7b6dd4b","tid":581734,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T01:39:45.000Z","msg":"餓狗搶屎"},{"pid":"8514683655987051fafc42eee3e9cc51b42f3733","tid":581734,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0